        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction & Isomerization reaction",
        "description": "在高压反应釜中，使用Ni/SAPO-11-A-6催化剂，在360°C、4.0 MPa氢气压力下，对油酸进行加氢和异构化反应4小时，生成异构烷烃（喷气燃料）。",
        "text_snippet": "Catalyst evaluation was performed in a high-pressure autoclave with a volume of 150 mL... In a typical reaction, 15 g of oleic acid and 0.7 g of catalyst were added into the reactor... The hydrogenation reaction was conducted for 4 h at different temperatures (300, 320, 340, 360, and 380 °C)... a maximum of 78.2% isomer selectivity was achieved by the Ni/SAPO-11-A-6 catalyst under reaction conditions of 360 °C, 4 h, and 4.0 MPa H₂.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrogenation reaction",
        "description": "催化剂制备的最后一步，将负载镍的催化剂前体在10% H₂/N₂气氛中于550°C下还原2小时，得到高分散的纳米镍催化剂。",
        "text_snippet": "the highly dispersed nano-7Ni/SAPO-11 catalyst was obtained after reduction under a 10% H₂/N₂ atmosphere at 550 °C for 2 h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
